title: gc: package name in identifiers in function type in error message
body:
build.go:68: cannot use func literal (type func() ([]os.FileInfo, error)) as type
func(build.dir string) (build.fi []os.FileInfo, build.err error) in assignment

should not be showing 'build.'
in fact should probably not be showing the names at all.
they are irrelevant to the type mismatch.
